    "title": "RewindBlockIndex reads chainActive (via ChainActive()) without holding cs_main",
    "body": "`RewindBlockIndex` reads `chainActive` (via `ChainActive()`) without holding `cs_main`:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/b2a6b0216192b6e8428f1a80b47f5178fccb961a/src/validation.cpp#L4314-L4331\r\n\r\n(Please note that callers of `RewindBlockIndex` are _not_ allowed to hold `cs_main` since `RewindBlockIndex` indirectly calls `LimitValidationInterfaceQueue`.)",
